OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA bright and largely dry day.
OL,6,FCloudier in the morning with just the
OL,7,Fslight chance of an isolated light
OL,8,Fshower in the west. Increasingly sunny
OL,9,Fspells developing through the day.
OL,10,FBreezy.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FDry with some bright or sunny
OL,13,Fspells in the evening. Staying dry in
OL,14,Fthe east overnight with clear spells.
OL,15,FTurning cloudier in the west
OL,16,Fovernight, with the odd light shower.
OL,17,
OL,18,CFriday:FDry with bright or sunny
OL,19,Fspells through much of the day,
OL,20,Fsomewhat cloudier in the west. Some
OL,21,Frain spreads east in the evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
